| VII | Security, Privacy & Data Residency | OAuth/OIDC; MFA; AccessPolicy / RBAC; Frankfurt residency; secrets in AWS SM | ✅ OIDC (provider decided in research); MFA + step-up (NFR-006); eu-central-1; AWS Secrets Manager |
